race.comment: DOONGALLA FLASH (8) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (25.80) at Ballarat. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from seven starts. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. MAMASAN (6) is an honest type who is lining up for her first start here. Comes here a winner after using the inside draw to advantage last time, scoring by 6 lengths at Warragul over 400m (22.87). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Expected to feature again. TORNADO TAHLIA (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (23.39) in a Mix 3/4 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. The form from her last run stacks up well. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. HOT SAKI (4) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.
